text: Itheum vittigerum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Francis Polkinghorne Pascoe in 1864. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Itheum vittigerum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1864
title: Itheum vittigerum
